longBusinessSummary: Kaisa Group Holdings Ltd., an investment holding company, engages in the property investment, development, and management businesses in the People's Republic of China. It develops commercial properties, such as office buildings, retail stores, and car parks. The company is also involved in the hotel and catering, cinema, and department stores and cultural center operations, as well as waterway passenger and cargo transportation, and healthcare business. Kaisa Group Holdings Ltd. was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, China.
